overview.en: ISC is the first global public chain of innovation and startup community, an innovation and startup service, incubation, investment support platform, a value realization tool for entrepreneur, investor and service provider, and it is also a whole ecological incubation on the chain.
overview.zh: 创链是首个面向区块链领域的创业、创新社区公链，区块链创新创业服务、孵化、投资的支撑平台，创业者、投资人、服务商的价值实现工具，创链是一个“链上全生态孵化器”。
